{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/en/hymn/h/1274",
  "title": "In Revelation two and three",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "In Revelation"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "two and"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "three,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "seven"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "local"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "churches"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "see:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "lessons"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "there for"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "you and"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "for the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord's re"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "cov"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "er"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "y."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The words to them are words to us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So that the church be glorious,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And all their warnings we must heed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So that the Lord can meet His need."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To Ephesus, the word is clear:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“To your first love you’re not so near;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’ve left to work so far away;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Repent, return to Him today.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, we must all turn back to Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Leave other loves, for these are sin."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, let us hearken to His call—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If we miss this, we’ve missed it all!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then unto Smyrna, suffering, sore—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“You have been tried, but something more—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be faithful unto death,” we’re told"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "(Not just of body but of soul)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be faithful ’til what’s natural dies;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your circumstances don’t despise;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord has sent them all to you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To prove that your first love is true."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From Pergamos we clearly see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The world has wed Christianity!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And faithful Antipas did fall—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He dared to stand against it all."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To wed the world we all must fear:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His spoken word will save us here—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If to His speaking we give heed,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll separated be indeed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then Thyatira comes at length:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Her mixture with the world her strength."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fine flour leavened by the yeast,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A harlot riding on a beast."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, we are mixed but hardly know;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To us this mixture fully show."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Each added thing we will refute"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Until we’re wholly absolute."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And then from Sardis, we can know"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is the way that we must go!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "She says she’s living, but she’s dead;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "She needs to touch the Lord instead."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, take us all the way to life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To overcome the deadness rife."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Away from deadness we would flee"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That full of life we’ll always be."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now Philadelphia comes at last;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That which she has she should hold fast"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The brothers’ love, the name, the word;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This church has satisfied the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We as the brothers all are one;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re one by life, and life alone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If we His word and name do keep"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A glorious building God will reap."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Laodicea warns us all:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From Philadelphia some will fall."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By saying, “I am rich,” it’s then"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord is outside wanting in."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lukewarmness we must ever spurn"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in the spirit always burn,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The inward life experience gain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And pay the price with Him to reign."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, shine Your light on us today"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we may fully go Your way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Anoint our eyes and let us see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So You can have recovery."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
